				</div>
				<div class="col entry_right">
						<h3><a href="http://www.huffingtonpost.com/ben-arnon/the-battle-for-gotham_b_9652014.html?utm_hp_ref=bernie-sanders" style="line-height: 18px !important;font-weight: bold;font-size: 16px;font-family: arial;color: #1A1A1A;">The Battle for Gotham (PHOTOS)</a></h3>
						<div class="green_entry_bar"></div>
				</div>
				<div class="clear"></div>
		                 	      			<p>In New York City there is a palpable energy in the air these days. I suspect the same holds true for upstate New York as well.  For the first time in decades, New York matters in the presidential election cycle.</p>
				 
		   <div class="author_bottom_desc">
			  <div class="blogger_img">
